<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= description %>">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gallery-white text-gallery-dark font-sans antialiased selection:bg-gallery-dark selection:text-white">
    
    <!-- Sticky Header -->
    <header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-gallery-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-gray-100 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 h-20 flex items-center justify-between">
            <!-- Logo -->
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase z-50">Cuatro Cuartos</a>
            
            <!-- Desktop Nav -->
            <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-12 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase">
                <a href="#collection" class="hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors">Colección</a>
                <a href="#about" class="hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors">Filosofía</a>
                <a href="#visit" class="hover:text-gray-500 transition-colors">Visítanos</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="bg-gallery-dark text-white px-6 py-2 hover:bg-black transition-colors">Contacto</a>
            </nav>

            <!-- Mobile Menu Button (Placeholder) -->
            <button class="md:hidden space-y-1.5 p-2 z-50">
                <div class="w-6 h-0.5 bg-current"></div>
                <div class="w-6 h-0.5 bg-current"></div>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1920px] mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-8 md:col-start-3 text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-light mb-8 leading-tight tracking-tight">
                    Muebles de autor,<br>espacios con alma.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
                    Diseño minimalista y texturas orgánicas inspiradas en la imperfección natural del Wabi-sabi. Fabricado artesanalmente en Tonalá.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="md:col-span-12 mt-12 md:mt-20">
                <div class="relative w-full aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[21/9] overflow-hidden bg-gray-100">
                    <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="Interior minimalista" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-[2s] hover:scale-105">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Collection Grid -->
    <section id="collection" class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1920px] mx-auto border-t border-gray-100">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-4">
            <div>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gray-400 block mb-2">Catálogo 2024</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-light">Piezas Seleccionadas</h2>
            </div>
            <a href="#" class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase border-b border-gallery-dark pb-1 hover:text-gray-600 hover:border-gray-600 transition-colors">Ver Todo</a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-16">
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                <div class="bg-gallery-gray aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
                     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors duration-500 z-10 w-full h-full"></div>
                    <img src="/images/gallery1.jpg" alt="Sillón Ōku" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-normal mb-1">Sillón Ōku</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Roble y Lino</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-sm font-light opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">↗</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div class="group cursor-pointer md:mt-12">
                <div class="bg-gallery-gray aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
                     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors duration-500 z-10 w-full h-full"></div>
                    <img src="/images/gallery2.jpg" alt="Mesa Kuri" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                 <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-normal mb-1">Mesa Kuri</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Concreto y Nogal</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-sm font-light opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">↗</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div class="group cursor-pointer">
                <div class="bg-gallery-gray aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
                     <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/0 group-hover:bg-black/5 transition-colors duration-500 z-10 w-full h-full"></div>
                    <img src="/images/gallery3.jpg" alt="Lámpara Hikari" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105">
                </div>
                 <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-normal mb-1">Lámpara Hikari</h3>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Cerámica</p>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-sm font-light opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300">↗</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer id="visit" class="bg-gallery-footer text-gray-400 py-24 px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
            
            <div class="md:col-span-4">
                <h4 class="text-white text-2xl font-light mb-8">Cuatro Cuartos</h4>
                <p class="font-light leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
                    Galería de diseño y mobiliario de autor. Creando espacios atemporales desde Tonalá, Jalisco.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-4 md:col-start-6">
                <h5 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white mb-8">Visítanos</h5>
                <address class="not-italic font-light space-y-2">
                    <p class="text-white">Av. Tonaltecas 123</p>
                    <p>Tonalá, Jalisco, México</p>
                    <p class="pt-4">Lun — Sáb: 10am — 7pm</p>
                </address>
                 <div class="mt-8">
                    <a href="mailto:contacto@cuatrocuartos.mx" class="block hover:text-white transition-colors">contacto@cuatrocuartos.mx</a>
                    <a href="tel:+523312345678" class="block hover:text-white transition-colors mt-2">+52 (33) 1234 5678</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="md:col-span-3">
                 <h5 class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-white mb-8">Newsletter</h5>
                 <form class="flex border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">
                     <input type="email" placeholder="Tu correo" class="bg-transparent w-full outline-none text-white placeholder-gray-600 font-light">
                     <button type="submit" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase hover:text-white transition-colors">Enviar</button>
                 </form>
            </div>

        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-[1920px] mx-auto mt-24 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs font-light tracking-wide opacity-60">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Cuatro Cuartos Galería</p>
            <div class="flex space-x-6 mt-4 md:mt-0">
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Instagram</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Facebook</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
